Right.

37:08.860 --> 37:11.663
And personally,
I think, maybe people...

37:11.697 --> 37:15.166
Women, my generation, might have
failed people like her

37:15.200 --> 37:16.968
by not passing things on.

37:17.002 --> 37:20.272
But now,
thanks to food bloggers,

37:20.306 --> 37:22.441
the younger ladies have...

37:22.474 --> 37:24.476
- An avenue to learn.
