creating a new society.

39:14.085 --> 39:14.585
♪

39:22.861 --> 39:26.398
Andela, cofounded by
Iyinoluwa Aboyeji

39:26.432 --> 39:29.334
and run in Nigeria
by Seni Sulyman,

39:29.367 --> 39:30.869
is a rigorous training program

39:30.902 --> 39:32.638
that teaches coders
and engineers

39:32.671 --> 39:34.339
with the goal
of creating no less

39:34.372 --> 39:36.475
than a continent-wide ecosystem

39:36.508 --> 39:38.644
of high-value
software developers.

39:38.677 --> 39:40.245
My mom had, like, a mobile shop,

39:40.278 --> 39:41.440
something like what's
in Computer Village,

39:41.447 --> 39:42.981
like, that's where I grew up.

39:43.014 --> 39:45.451
She'll see mobile phones,
they'll fix it there,

39:45.484 --> 39:47.185
and she just used to run that.

39:47.218 --> 39:49.421
I tried other, like, jobs,
but the jobs I got,

39:49.455 --> 39:51.389
I'm like, no, I don't want
to be a salesperson.

39:51.423 --> 39:52.991
I don't want to be a secretary.

39:54.926 --> 39:56.895
So that's why
I got into programming.

39:56.928 --> 40:00.699
Shalom and Blessing
are trainees in the program,

40:00.732 --> 40:04.369
people who will someday
rewrite the way Africa works.

40:04.402 --> 40:07.739
As you can see, there are a
lot of issues in Nigeria today.

40:07.773 --> 40:09.641
The average Nigerian is
struggling to...

40:09.675 --> 40:12.277
Just food, water,
clothing, shelter.

40:12.310 --> 40:14.045
We all believe that
this will change,

40:14.079 --> 40:16.314
and we all believe that
we will change that.

40:16.347 --> 40:17.916
In the U.S.,
for every software developer

40:17.949 --> 40:20.586
that's looking for a job,
there are five openings,

40:20.619 --> 40:22.113
which means there's
a massive opportunity

40:22.120 --> 40:24.556
to get these awesome people,
who are really smart

40:24.590 --> 40:27.626
and really driven, to be ready
to take on Africa's challenges.

40:27.659 --> 40:29.360
But that's what's special
about this place.

40:29.394 --> 40:31.429
I mean, most people are
kind of resigned

40:31.463 --> 40:33.565
to the reality that...
That they have.

40:33.599 --> 40:35.400
We're creating
an alternate reality

40:35.433 --> 40:38.737
where there's always gonna be
power for you to do your work.

40:38.770 --> 40:40.038
- Yeah.
- You know...

40:41.707 --> 40:44.042
Africa, it should be stressed,
is home to seven

40:44.075 --> 40:46.578
of the ten fastest growing
Internet populations

40:46.612 --> 40:48.346
in the world

40:48.379 --> 40:52.250
with a huge young
and mostly untapped labor pool

40:52.283 --> 40:54.653
of eager and ambitious people.

40:54.686 --> 40:58.356
